title: VA Easy Pop September 2013 - Music Box (Dutch Treat I1 XHQ)
description:
The ninth and last Indie Playlist of September 2013 has become - to be completely honest - a bit dull. It happens sometimes when you have enough good tracks (especially at the monthly round up) and cannot get that personal spark into the list. However its not about me and the songs are simply good. So you might like it...... Enjoy,
